# Marketing Mix Modeling (MMM)

## Business Objective
Quantify ROI of each marketing channel and optimize 
budget allocation to maximize revenue using Bayesian MMM.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.11 | PyMC | Pandera | Plotly | Power BI

## Project Phases
- [x] Phase 1 — Repository Setup
- [x] Phase 2 — Data Ingestion & Schema Validation
- [ ] Phase 3 — Exploratory Data Analysis
- [ ] Phase 4 — Feature Engineering
- [ ] Phase 5 — Bayesian MMM Modeling
- [ ] Phase 6 — Budget Optimization
- [ ] Phase 7 — Power BI Dashboard
- [ ] Phase 8 — GA4 & Forecastiny
